name: Australian Shepherd
info: Australian shepherds are known for their boundless energy and gorgeous coat.

name: Siberian Husky
info: The Siberian husky is a medium-sized dog, slightly longer than tall.

name: Pembroke Welsh Corgi
info: Pembroke Welsh corgis are beloved for their short legs and lively, comedic personalities.

name: Rottweiler
info: Rottweilers are in the working group of dog breeds, meaning that they thrive when they have an activity or “job.”

name: Cavalier King Charles Spaniel
info: Cavalier King Charles spaniels are not as regal and standoffish as their name may suggest.

name: Shih Tzu
info: Shih Tzus are part of the toy group and are adored for their short stature, playful personalities and cute hairstyles.
